      "title": "[DC] lightproud@🔸校貓日誌┊schoolcat’s-notes: We've noted and looked into the concerns that have been raised: the opening of a",
      "summary": "We've noted and looked into the concerns that have been raised: the opening of a gameplay trailer released in July 2026 for a certain game bears a strong resemblance to our PV \"Silver\" (released November 2023), both in composition and sound design. We've completed a side-by-side comparison of the visuals and audio, documented and preserved the relevant materials along with both release timelines, and handed the matter over to a professional team to assess how best to proceed. We'll keep you posted as things develop.\n\nAs the producer of Morimens, and as someone who's been a devoted fan of that game's original series for years, coming across something like this leaves me with genuinely complicated feelings. What I'm most grateful for is that you all cared enough to speak up: It reminds us just how much responsibility we carry.\n\nAs a token of thanks for your support, we'll be releasing a 4K wallpaper of this specific CG from \"Silver\" for everyone to keep. We'll do everything we can to live up to your expectations and keep pushing forward.\n\nMay the Silver Key light our path.\n[附件: D0112497-5670-4DAD-B287-D5EFED76635A-47358-000029C0C5C644CF.png]",
